  27 Aug 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org>
  graveman-0.3.12_p4-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  16 Jul 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> graveman-0.3.12_p4-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

  13 Jul 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org>
  graveman-0.3.12_p4-r1.ebuild:
  added ~ppc64

*graveman-0.3.12_p4-r1 (11 Jul 2005)

  11 Jul 2005; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  +files/joliet-long.patch, +graveman-0.3.12_p4-r1.ebuild:
  Include patch to invoke cdrecord with the "-joliet-long" option.
  Patch provided by Federico Galassi in #98619.

  07 Jul 2005; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  graveman-0.3.12_p4.ebuild:
  Stable on x86 and ppc.

  14 Jun 2005; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  graveman-0.3.11.ebuild, -graveman-0.3.12.ebuild,
  -graveman-0.3.12_p2.ebuild, -graveman-0.3.12_p3.ebuild,
  graveman-0.3.12_p4.ebuild:
  Clean up.
  Fixed libglade dependency. graveman requires libglade >=2.4,
  as reported by Martin Grosshauser in #96085.

  10 Jun 2005; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> graveman-0.3.11.ebuild,
  graveman-0.3.12.ebuild, graveman-0.3.12_p2.ebuild,
  graveman-0.3.12_p3.ebuild, graveman-0.3.12_p4.ebuild:
  Changing mad->mp3; bug #94045.

